# LLM strategy documents

The `docs/llm/` directory contains strategy and architecture notes about the
AI/prompt/gateway logic.

The `docs/schemas/` directory contains the canonical human-readable schema docs
for build profiles, scaffold contracts, and integration/data schema surfaces.

## Key files

- `docs/llm/AC-schema.txt` - Acceptance criteria for AI/gateway logic
- `docs/llm/v0-prompt-guide.txt` - v0 prompt best practices
- `docs/llm/DEPS-STATUS.txt` - Dependency versions and known issues
- `docs/schemas/README.md` - Schema index and source-of-truth map

## When to consult

Read these when changing AI/gateway/prompt-assist logic. After making
such changes, update the relevant docs/llm/ files to keep them in sync.
